---
config:
  look: handDrawn
  theme: neutral
---
graph TB
    Holders["xOGN Holders<br/>(staked OGN)"]
    Gov["Origin DeFi Governance<br/>24h delay + 48h voting"]
    Timelock["Timelock Controller<br/>48h delay"]
    ARM["ARM Contract<br/>(admin surface)"]
    Multisig["GOV Multisig 5-of-8<br/>CANCELLER only"]
    Operator["Operator EOA<br/>no timelock"]
    CrossPrice["Cross-price bound<br/>48h timelocked"]

    Holders -->|100K xOGN to propose| Gov
    Gov -->|schedule| Timelock
    Timelock -->|execute ~5d total| ARM
    Multisig -.->|can cancel| Timelock
    ARM -.->|upgrade, set cross-price,<br/>grant operator| ARM
    Operator -->|set buy/sell prices| ARM
    CrossPrice -.->|bounds| Operator

    classDef central fill:#a5d8ff,color:#0c0c0c,stroke:#0c0c0c,stroke-width:2px
    classDef protected fill:#a5d8ff,color:#0c0c0c,stroke:#0c0c0c,stroke-width:2px
    classDef unprotected fill:#ffc9c9,color:#0c0c0c,stroke:#0c0c0c,stroke-width:2px
    class ARM central
    class Timelock,CrossPrice protected
    class Operator unprotected
